{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 REAPER Scripts by Mike Pierluissi\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 LoopIt\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Looping media items based on a trimmed item and user input crossfade length in seconds.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Spread to Markers\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Spread single or groups of items across markers in a REAPER project.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Super Glue\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Bounce-in-place groups of media items and track FX to a new track while muting the originals.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 Track Renamer\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Single or batch renaming of tracks with a myriad of features.\par}
